data.name: PersonalityLabel.ToolTip
data.value:
Completely invisible stats regarding your monster's personality. We're not 100% if the names are correct, but the current nomenclature is:
Temprement, Pride, Proactive, Desire, Sensitivity, Competitiveness, Seriousness, and Self Control.

data.name: SpoilLabel.ToolTip
data.value: One of two values contributing to the heart bar. Increases by spoiling your monster, as the name suggests. Resting for four weeks at the start of a new monster's life is an easy way to raise this.

data.name: ProteinLabel.ToolTip
data.value: One of the three hidden values behind the Nutrition score on food. Decreases by 1 each week. If you're stuck on what to feed: Nuts and Carrots on a budget, and Vine Grass if you're well off and your monster is at least 2 happiness to it.
